@Microservice.Discount.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5093
@code = DISCOUNT15

### Get Discount By Code
GET {{Microservice.Discount.Api_HostAddress}}/v1/discount/{{code}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Create Discount
POST {{Microservice.Discount.Api_HostAddress}}/v1/discount
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "DISCOUNT15",
  "rate": 0.15,
  "userId": "3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6",
  "expireDate": "2026-12-31T23:59:59Z"
}

###

### Create Discount - Higher Rate
POST {{Microservice.Discount.Api_HostAddress}}/v1/discount
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "SUMMER50",
  "rate": 0.50,
  "userId": "898688f4-de46-415f-a393-9e73b8fb3bd1",
  "expireDate": "2026-08-31T23:59:59Z"
}

###

### Create Discount - Invalid Rate (Validation Error)
POST {{Microservice.Discount.Api_HostAddress}}/v1/discount
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "INVALID",
  "rate": 1.5,
  "userId": "3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6",
  "expireDate": "2026-12-31T23:59:59Z"
}

